    "Our model yielded better accuracy results, such as an increase of about 1.34% in the 6-class division.",
    "The consistency of improved performance in all divisions showcases the broad applicability of our model.",
    "As for the work of Goyal et al.",
    "31, they only classified into a 2-class division (N, D) using the DFU dataset.",
    "When tested on the AZH dataset, our model demonstrated 100% accuracy, similar to their findings."
